8. Stacks Explorer, Testnet Tools & Deployment Resources

A production deployment on Stacks relies on a full ecosystem of utilities:

Essential tools:

Stacks Explorer → contract verification & public tracking

Testnet Faucet → acquire STX for testing

Contract Verifier → validate smart contracts publicly

Devnet CLI → spin up dockerized environment

Hiro Developer Console → manage API keys & analytics

Useful for debugging, validating user activity, and monitoring your deployment.
